Base class for React class components. Provides lifecycle methods, `this.state`, `this.props`, and `this.setState()`. Function components with hooks are now the recommended approach.

```jsx
class MyComponent extends React.PureComponent<Props, State> {
  render() { return <div />; }
}
```
Similar to `Component` but implements `shouldComponentUpdate()` with a shallow prop and state comparison. Skips re-renders when props and state are shallowly equal.
